You are practically certain that West holds the two outstanding clubs. If he also holds the diamond Ace, all is lost.|
PG| ***** 25 ***** |


CP|8|at| When West plays low on the diamond lead, you have reason to hope.|
pg| ***** 26 ***** |


cp||pc|D9|
